com.badlogic.gdx.input.recorder

Interface InputRecordReader

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    JsonInputRecordReader, RandomInputRecordReader

    public interface InputRecordReader
    Interface for classes that provide access to a stream of data describing changes to an instance of Input. This does not necessarily mean that the supplied data is from a record. For example, the RandomInputRecordReader generates this data on the fly
